<!-- Oasis Project -->
<section id='oasis-project'>
  <div class='background-image'>
    <div class='container'>
      <div id='oasis-quote' class='row'>
        <h1 class='pull-left'>the <span>OASIS</span> project</h1>
        <blockquote class='pull-left'>
          <p><em>To solve the problem, you must see the problem.</em></p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      <div class='row' id='oasis-description'>
        <div class='col-sm-11 hidden-xs' id='long-description'>
          <p>The goal of the Oasis project is to help make environmental and health problems <span class='underline'>visible</span>. The Oasis project aims to reveal threats that are imperceptible to the human eye, like heavy metal contaminants in water or high blood pressure. Crowd-sourcing that data will empower communities to tackle widespread environmental and health challenges that require collective action to solve.</p>
        </div>
        <div class='col-xs-12 visible-xs' id='short-description'>
          <p>The Oasis project is an experiment in citizen science, an attempt to build a "living map" of shared knowledge built from individual contributions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


